{"tid":1794450,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[正能量] 請各位手足唔好放棄任何一種攬炒手段","createTime":"2019-12-23T06:16:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T06:28:09.000Z","uid":111253,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a9a12bfdad6da1b8101d6a5d8b4a2177dd6e8279","tid":1794450,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T06:16:15.000Z","msg":"團結就是力量, 或者你會屌人付出唔夠多, 但要明白多管齊下先可以達致攬炒<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃色經濟圈：</span></strong><br />\n杯葛藍店, 直接冇左批黃客<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">和你SHOP/ 大型集會上街：</span></strong><br />\n地區性癱瘓經濟/大型商場, 黑警進場, 迫你落閘, 冇人流冇消費, 影響租金等等<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">裝修：</span></strong><br />\n開唔到鋪唔知幾多日既成本, 維修成本等等<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好迷信「對家大集團, 大把HP, 我地點削血都冇用啦」<br />\n我明白好似打機咁, 你永遠見唔到BOSS血條唔知打到幾時先完,<br />\n但以上所有野都講緊錢, 我總唔信大集團有無限資金, <br />\n成績表要等, 雖然而家見唔到咩大成果, <br />\n但繼續堅持落去, 我唔信聖誕新年過後班仆街仲頂得住<br />\n無論你抗爭成本有幾多都好, <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">朝住「攬炒」呢個目標實冇死, 能力範圍下盡做</span></strong><br />\n祝各位手足武運昌隆"},{"pid":"68a7267309263358edf4143d83882cc4b4f1b85f","tid":1794450,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T06:20:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a33879f9985e7bc768e309a00613d1ce7aaff6","tid":1794450,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T06:21:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f680e9ec5078bd937bf2cb36b813845994195d3a","tid":1794450,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T06:23:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9be2d036f2c6d0c3c59df69f7bad69d038bc103","tid":1794450,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T06:23:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b566a090c2f53